      of the stack.  Earlier-registered listeners still run (they have
      to ŌĆö Playwright/JS does not let us mutate listener order at
      runtime), but they return immediately if they are not the top.
    - Same module is used by both the drawer (via c_yui_shell.js) and
      the modal/dialog helpers (shell_modals.js), so the stack
      naturally arbitrates between any layered overlays.
    
