           EV_END_TASK BEFORE calling gobj_stop on itself, so we get the
           event with src == priv->gobj_task while it is still RUNNING.
           Stopping it here would double-stop and log "GObj NOT RUNNING".
         - watchdog: src is c_auth_bff itself, the task is still running,
           and we must force-stop it.
