    ================
    Reuses the phase-enum dispatch pattern from test9.  One
    priv->gobj_http_cl slot is reused for http_cl #1 then #2 ŌĆö after
    stop_tree'ing the first, the slot is simply overwritten with the
    fresh gobj; the stopped old tree hangs off the driver as a dead
    child until yuno teardown, same as every other test.
    
    Two small helpers are extracted from the body to keep the phase
    transitions readable:
      - open_new_http_cl(gobj)  ŌĆö creates a C_PROT_HTTP_CL + C_TCP stack
                                  and start_tree's it
      - post_login(gobj)        ŌĆö builds the POST /auth/login query and
                                  sends it on priv->gobj_http_cl
    
    Both are static inside c_test11_cancel_retry.c ŌĆö they only make
    sense inside this particular two-connection dance; no candidate for
    promotion into test_helpers yet.
    
