    logout fix and future-proofs against any Keycloak build that starts
    returning 201 Created / 202 Accepted / etc.  The actual error path
    in result_token_response (HTTP 400 to the browser on !=200) is
    unchanged: it still rejects anything the spec doesn't promise.
    
